$6: USER PREFERENCES

!:output_format{cond:"always", acc:"Tables > lists > K/V > PUML diagrams > prose. If information fits in a table, it IS a table. Prose is last resort", status:"current"}
!:communication{cond:"always", acc:"LLM->human is structured, not prose. No ASCII art — PUML exclusively. Documentation without ASCII diagrams", status:"current"}
!:learning_model{cond:"always", acc:"4-stage cognitive model (unconscious incompetence -> unconscious competence) mapped to SES->LNG->KNW. Maturation: detect_recurrence(3) -> ask_user -> promote/decay", status:"current"}
!:hcortex_rules{cond:"always", acc:"HCORTEX = decompression rules to standard .md, not an extension. brain.cortex = local brain. AGENTS.md = HCORTEX in user language", status:"current"}
!:no_model_mention{cond:"always", acc:"Never mention the LLM model name. No 'running on DeepSeek', 'as a Claude model', etc", status:"current"}

